---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
export const prerender = true;
<Base title="Terms and Conditions | Golf Graeagle" description="Terms and Conditions for GolfGraeagle.com — Zoomaway Technologies Inc. User Agreement governing use of the site and booking services.">
  <Nav />
  <div style="min-height:100vh;padding:140px 48px 80px;max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p style="font-size:11px;color:#e8a850;letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:0 0 16px;">Legal</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(36px,5vw,56px);font-weight:500;color:#f0f8f2;margin:0 0 12px;line-height:1.1;">Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(240,248,242,0.3);margin:0 0 56px;">GolfGraeagle.com · Zoomaway Technologies Inc. User Agreement</p>
    </div>

    <div style="font-size:15px;color:rgba(240,248,242,0.65);line-height:1.8;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:36px;">

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#f0f8f2;margin:0 0 14px;">Terms of Use — Zoomaway Technologies Inc. User Agreement</h2>
        <p>Thank you for visiting with Zoomaway ("Zoomaway") or one of its subsidiaries (Tripsee), or for using one of our web based products (<a href="https://golfthehighsierra.com" style="color:#e8a850;">Golfthehighsierra.com</a>, <a href="https://groupgolftours.com" style="color:#e8a850;">Groupgolftours.com</a>, <a href="https://golfgraeagle.com" style="color:#e8a850;">Golfgraeagle.com</a>).</p>
        <p style="margin-top:14px;">This User Agreement (the "Agreement") describes the terms and conditions governing your usage of the Zoomaway owned sites (the "Sites"). By using the Sites and buying through the Sites, you agree to be bound by its terms and conditions. If you do not agree to be bound by these terms and conditions, please do not use or access the Sites. Zoomaway may change the Terms of Use at any time as provided in this Agreement or otherwise.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#f0f8f2;margin:0 0 14px;">1. Use of the Sites</h2>
        <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;">
          <p><strong style="color:rgba(240,248,242,0.8);">a.</strong> You must read, agree with, and accept all of the terms and conditions contained in this Agreement and Zoomaway's Privacy Policy, which are hereby incorporated by reference before you may use the Sites.</p>
          <p><strong style="color:rgba(240,248,242,0.8);">b.</strong> You must be a natural person, 18 years or older. A corporation, partnership, Limited Liability Company or any other form of entity cannot become a user or member. You may not use machines, scripts, or automated services. You may maintain only one account. Zoomaway may cancel any duplicate accounts at its sole and absolute discretion. You agree to make reservations only for yourself or for another person who authorizes you to make such reservation.</p>
          <p><strong style="color:rgba(240,248,242,0.8);">c.</strong> You must have Internet access and a valid email address to book. Zoomaway is not responsible for your inability to connect to the Internet, to log onto the Sites, or to access your Zoomaway account.</p>
          <p><strong style="color:rgba(240,248,242,0.8);">d.</strong> By signing up to receive our electronic newsletters, book reservations and/or creating an account, you agree to receive email communications that are account, membership and travel-related. The travel-related emails will highlight special deals that are available to Zoomaway's customers. You can opt-out of receiving promotional travel-related emails by either visiting your account page to edit your profile or following the unsubscribe link on any of the travel-related emails you receive. If you booked reservations and/or created an account, you may not opt-out of communications which are account related and not promotional in nature. If you do not wish to receive them, you have the option to deactivate your account.</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#f0f8f2;margin:0 0 14px;">2. Account Access and Transferability</h2>
        <p>Upon your registration as a customer, you will provide your email address and a password that will allow you to access your account on the Sites, verify activity, change or cancel reservations, and manage personal information. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your password and account. You are fully responsible for all activities that occur using your password or account. Please notify Zoomaway immediately of any unauthorized use of your password or account or any other breach of security.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#f0f8f2;margin:0 0 14px;">3. Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <p>Standard cancellation window is 72 hours for individual bookings. Large group outings are governed by individual contracts. See our full <a href="/cancellation-policy" style="color:#e8a850;">Cancellation Policy</a> for details. Zoomaway will pass on vendor (host) cancellation policies to customers where applicable.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#f0f8f2;margin:0 0 14px;">4. Content and Conduct</h2>
        <p>You are solely responsible for any content you submit to the Sites. Zoomaway Technologies Inc. and its subsidiaries are not responsible for offensive content posted by users. Our products are a solicitation for business purposes. Any use of our products for personal purposes or illegal activities is strictly prohibited. Zoomaway Inc. staff will report any abuses to the proper authorities.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:500;color:#f0f8f2;margin:0 0 14px;">5. Governing Sites</h2>
        <p>This Agreement applies to the following Zoomaway web products: GolfGraeagle.com, GolftheHighSierra.com, and GroupGolfTours.com, and their associated booking and travel services.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="reveal" style="border-top:1px solid rgba(240,248,242,0.06);padding-top:36px;">
        <p style="font-size:13px;color:rgba(240,248,242,0.3);">Questions about these terms? Contact: <a href="mailto:sean@zoomaway.com" style="color:#e8a850;">sean@zoomaway.com</a></p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
  <Footer />
</Base>
